WEBVTT

00:00:03.167 --> 00:00:06.103
Shah Rukh Khan: There was a neighbor
I had in Delhi

00:00:06.127 --> 00:00:10.183
who never found any boy
suitable enough for his daughter.

00:00:10.207 --> 00:00:15.583
So one day we finally asked him:
What he was looking for?

00:00:15.607 --> 00:00:17.846
Did he think some prince
charming would arrive?

00:00:17.870 --> 00:00:19.783
He very simply replied,

00:00:19.807 --> 00:00:23.863
“I want her to be with someone who can
honour this relationship for a lifetime,

00:00:23.887 --> 00:00:25.663
with love.”

00:00:25.687 --> 00:00:30.303
This was an apt answer, I thought,